# Platform runners. android/ & ios/ are now COMMITTED — the app ships native
# home-screen widget code (iOS WidgetKit extension + Android receiver) that must
# live in version control. Build artifacts inside them are excluded by
# android/.gitignore and ios/.gitignore. The unused desktop/web runners are still
# generated locally with `flutter create`, so stay ignored.
/linux/
/macos/
/windows/
/web/
